\c 25
\s Izigaba zabatshayi bezinto zokuhlabelela
\p
\v 1 UDavida lenduna zebutho\x + 9.11. Seb. 4.1.\x* behlukanisela-ke inkonzo emadodaneni kaAsafi\x + 6.39.\x* lakaHemani\x + 6.33.\x* lakaJeduthuni\x + 16.41. 6.44.\x*, abaprofetha\x + 25.2,3. 1 Sam. 10.11. 19.24. Neh. 12.8. Eks. 15.20. 2 Kho. 3.15. 1 Kor. 14.24,26.\x* ngamachacho\x + 25.6. 15.16. Neh. 12.27.\x*, ngezigubhu zezintambo\x + 25.6. 15.16. Neh. 12.27.\x*, langensimbi ezincencethayo\x + 25.6. 15.16. Neh. 12.27.\x*. Lenani lamadoda omsebenzi lalinjengokwenkonzo yawo:
\v 2 Emadodaneni kaAsafi\x + 6.39.\x*: OZakuri loJosefa loNethaniya loAsarela, amadodana kaAsafi\x + Neh. 12.35.\x*, phansi kwesandla sikaAsafi, owaprofetha ngokwesandla senkosi\x + 25.2,3. 1 Sam. 10.11. 19.24. Neh. 12.8. Eks. 15.20. 2 Kho. 3.15. 1 Kor. 14.24,26.\x*.
\v 3 NgoJeduthuni: Amadodana kaJeduthuni: OGedaliya, loZeri, loJeshaya, uHashabhiya, loMathithiya, beyisithupha, ezandleni zikayise uJeduthuni\x + 16.41. 6.44.\x*, owayeprofetha ngechacho, ukubonga lokudumisa iN\nd kosi\x + 25.2,3. 1 Sam. 10.11. 19.24. Neh. 12.8. Eks. 15.20. 2 Kho. 3.15. 1 Kor. 14.24,26.\x*\nd*.
\v 4 NgoHemani: Amadodana kaHemani: OBukhiya, uMathaniya, uUziyeli, uShebuweli, loJerimothi, uHananiya, uHanani, uEliyatha, uGidaliti, loRomamiti-Ezeri, uJoshibekasha, uMaloti, uHothiri, uMahaziyothi\x + 6.33.\x*.
\v 5 Bonke laba babengamadodana kaHemani umboni wenkosi emazwini kaNkulunkulu ukuphakamisa uphondo. Njalo uNkulunkulu wamnika uHemani amadodana alitshumi lane lamadodakazi amathathu\x + 2 Sam. 24.11.\x*.
\v 6 Bonke laba babesezandleni zikayise ekuhlabeleleni endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* ngensimbi ezincencethayo\x + 25.6. 15.16. Neh. 12.27.\x*, izigubhu zezintambo\x + 25.6. 15.16. Neh. 12.27.\x*, lamachacho\x + 25.6. 15.16. Neh. 12.27.\x* enkonzweni yendlu kaNkulunkulu, phansi kwesandla senkosi, oAsafi\x + 6.39.\x* loJeduthuni\x + 16.41. 6.44.\x* loHemani\x + 6.33.\x*.
\v 7 Lenani labo kanye labafowabo ababefundiswe ngezingoma zeN\nd kosi\nd*, bonke ababelolwazi\x + 25.8. 2 Lan. 23.13.\x*, lalingamakhulu amabili lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lesificaminwembili\x + 23.5.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Basebesenza inkatho yokuphosa ngomlindo\x + 26.16. 26.12. Neh. 12.24.\x*, omncinyane njengomkhulu, ofundisayo lofundayo\x + 25.8. 2 Lan. 23.13.\x*.
\v 9 Inkatho yokuqala yasiphumela uAsafi\x + 24.7.\x* kuJosefa\x + 25.2.\x*; eyesibili kuGedaliya\x + 25.3.\x*, yena labafowabo lamadodana akhe, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.9.\x*;
\v 10 eyesithathu \add k\add*uZakuri\x + 25.2.\x*, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.9.\x*;
\v 11 eyesine kuIziri, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.3.\x*;
\v 12 eyesihlanu \add k\add*uNethaniya, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.2.\x*;
\v 13 eyesithupha \add k\add*uBukhiya, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 14 eyesikhombisa \add k\add*uAsarela, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.2.\x*;
\v 15 eyesificaminwembili \add k\add*uJeshaya, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.3.\x*;
\v 16 eyesificamunwemunye \add k\add*uMathaniya, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 17 eyetshumi \add k\add*uShimeyi, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.3.\x*;
\v 18 eyetshumi lanye \add k\add*uAzareli, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 19 eyetshumi lambili kuHashabhiya, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.3.\x*;
\v 20 eyetshumi lantathu \add k\add*uShebuweli, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 21 eyetshumi lane \add k\add*uMathithiya, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.3.\x*;
\v 22 eyetshumi lanhlanu kuJeremothi, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4. 23.23. 24.30.\x*;
\v 23 eyetshumi lesithupha kuHananiya, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 24 eyetshumi lesikhombisa kuJoshibekasha, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 25 eyetshumi lesificaminwembili kuHanani, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 26 eyetshumi lesificamunwemunye kuMalothi, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 27 eyamatshumi amabili kuEliyatha, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 28 eyamatshumi amabili lanye kuHothiri, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 29 eyamatshumi amabili lambili kuGidaliti, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 30 eyamatshumi amabili lantathu kuMahaziyothi, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*;
\v 31 eyamatshumi amabili lane kuRomamiti-Ezeri, amadodana akhe labafowabo, belitshumi lambili\x + 25.4.\x*.